      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Go down with me; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " because Jerusalem was in a mountainous part of the country, and much of it built upon a hill. ",
