        "text": "holders of power among you, i.e.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " those who are invested with the requisite official power (for making a public complaint in the name of the Jewish nation). Thus the usual literal meaning of ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "δυνατός",
        "children": []
